# useTheme

`useTheme` is a custom hook used to get the theme object from context.

## Import

```jsx live=false
import { useTheme } from '@totejs/uikit';
```

## Usage

```jsx live=false
function Example() {
  const theme = useTheme();

  return <div>{/* Do something with the theme */}</div>;
}
```

